Subject: Hirano body
Value: < intracellular aggregates of actin and actin-associated proteins first observed in neurons (nerve cells) by Asao Hirano. PMID: 21978358>

Subject: nephrogenic metaplasia
Value: .A rare benign neoplasm of the mucosa of the urinary bladder or the urethra, consisting of tubular structures resembling those of the nephron.

Subject: angiofibroma
Value: .A benign neoplasm of fibrous tissue in which there are multiple large and small dilated vascular channels ( M9160/0).

Subject: granulosa cell tumor
Value: . Derived from sex cord stromal cells. In male thought to be Sertoli cells. (M- 8620/1).
